{"tid":2046268,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【脫支一鋪清】拒絕中國監控！ 印度「移除中國APP」爆紅2週下載破百萬","createTime":"2020-06-01T09:45:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T12:42:05.000Z","uid":242537,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b952a3e27af315a665477e4a88757e8e3da6ae7b","tid":2046268,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T09:45:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3183835\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3183835&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8zBezIcYxRdZTJmtLZSysqE%3D&h=eac03098\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3183835&h=80044356\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3183835</a><br />\n<br />\n外界長期以來對中國手機APP及部分3C產品抱有疑慮，認為有暴露個資、侵犯隱私的風險。在中國與印度邊界緊張情勢升高、國際間因武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）疫情而反中情緒高漲之際，印度一家軟體公司推出「移除中國 APP」（Remove China APP）手機應用程式，號稱能移除手機內所有由中國公司開發的APP，一炮而紅，短短兩週內下載量已經突破百萬！<br />\n<br />\n由印度OneTouch AppLabs公司推出的這款免費APP，目前只有安卓（Android）版本，在Google PLAY商店已有超過13萬則評論，總體評分高達4.8分（滿分5分）。據介紹，這款軟體不收費，也不會要求取得任何手機使用權限。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，中國App竊取個資早已不是秘密。早在2017年，印度政府就公布了42款有資安風險的中國手機App，認為這些都是間諜程式，並表示這些軟體會把用戶資料傳到中國境內的伺服器，將會影響國防安全，呼籲軍方查證刪除。對此當時有些公司也出面澄清，表示自己並非中國的公司。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/06/01/phptb9RSp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F06%2F01%2Fphptb9RSp.jpg&h=2d76f461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「移除中國APP」手機應用程式，一推出就大受歡迎。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.chinaappsremover&amp;hl=en_US\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.chinaappsremover%26hl%3Den_US&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns8zBezIcYxRdZTJmtLZSysqE%3D&h=27f7d6a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.chinaappsremover&amp;hl=en_US</a>"},{"pid":"176dc6c0fecd595e7332132362c52c6a13672b6e","tid":2046268,"uid":242537,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T09:46:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mb2BoK8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMb2BoK8.jpg&h=9167de3d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"06e446a2c5fa700dd40fbd2d709bd73a1594faf0","tid":2046268,"uid":55010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T09:49:11.000Z","msg":"DL唔到！！"},{"pid":"975a14705d2dfd883e58798882cf5c77a1f1e57d","tid":2046268,"uid":349744,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T12:42:05.000Z","msg":"IOS應該係整唔到呢隻app㗎<br />\n因為我2個月前真係研究過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nios permission問題，睇唔到device裝咗咩其他app<br />\n<br />\n另外有人話香港人冇創意整唔到呢啲app<br />\n但其實3月頭已經有人諗到呢個idea同我講<br />\n只係我當時趕𡁵ios版所以唔得閒整<br />\n所以唔好睇少香港人<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1kRVFgX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1kRVFgX.png&h=9aeedcf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n又有人話不如list晒啲app出嚟自己睇自己del啦<br />\n咁我隻「共業」就咁你啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2043194/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2043194/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n又見咁多人android版download唔到<br />\ndownload完又未必check得晒 (因為佢主要target印度market嘅app)<br />\n所以我開始整𡁵呢個function<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家快啲鞭撻我等我寫快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}